The Middle East is getting olderWhy I'm optimistic about the waning of conflict in the region. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-middle-east-is-getting golder https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-middle-east-is-getting golderNoah Smith Sun, 05 Nov 2023 02:16:18 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg" width="1024" height="768" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:768,&quot;width&quot;:1024,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:519992,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption">由<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=17138401">叙利亚框架</a>（Pro-FSA信息） -  [1]，CC由2.0</figcaption></figure></div><p>我注意到关于以色列加沙战争的有趣事物似乎普遍被忽略了：这场战争并没有显示出在整个中东地区蔓延的太多迹象。也门的胡西（Houthis）（伊朗的一位民兵之一）在以色列的一般方向上发射了几枚导弹，并发出了<a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/features/2023/11/2/analysis-houthis-declare-war-on-israel-but-their-real-target-is-elsewhere">战争宣言</a>，但似乎没有人非常担心。真主党是2006年与以色列战斗的黎巴嫩民兵，他<a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/world-news/2023/11/03/hassan-nasrallah-hezbollah-speech-oct-7-hamas-iran-israel/">选择远离</a>冲突，就像伊朗本身一样。每个人都在2000年代初期担心的“阿拉伯街”肯定有抗议，以支持巴勒斯坦人，但<a href="https://carnegieendowment.org/2023/11/01/pay-attention-to-arab-public-response-to-israel-hamas-war-pub-90893">他们非常和平</a>。沙特阿拉伯表示，<a href="https://www.axios.com/2023/10/31/saudi-megadeal-normalization-israel-biden">它仍然希望使与以色列的关系正常</a>于停火。</p><p>这是一个很好的迹象，这远非每个人都在战争的头几天抛弃的可怕期望。 2011年，阿拉伯之春像野火一样蔓延开来，在叙利亚和也门点燃了巨大的，漫长的，流血的战争，以及整个中东的各种较小的战争。以色列加沙战争没有表现出重复这一历史的迹象。</p><p>当然，可能有很多原因。经过二十年的战争，该地区可能会精疲力尽。<a href="https://taskandpurpose.com/news/two-navy-aircraft-carriers-mediterranean/">美国的威慑</a>可能是限制伊朗的手和代理人的手。以色列 - 巴勒斯坦冲突对该地区可能不像伊朗和沙特阿拉伯之间的长期冷战那么重要。 ETC。</p><p>但是我认为人口衰老也可能与之有关。有一个非常公认的文献，将年轻人口的凸起与升高冲突的风险联系起来。当然，这种链接只是一个相关性 - 显然很难找到改变国家年龄结构的自然实验，而不是战争本身。但这是一个相当完善的相关性。例如， <a href="https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-030-73065-9_3">Cincotta和Weber（2021）</a>发现，中位年龄为25岁以下的国家更有可能进行革命： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg" width="668" height="460.16157205240177" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:631,&quot;width&quot;:916,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:668,&quot;bytes&quot;:79076,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-030-73065-9_3">Cincotta和Weber（2021）</a></figcaption></figure></div><p> <a href="https://academic.oup.com/isq/article/50/3/607/1800827?login=false">Urdal（2006）</a>发现：</p><blockquote><p>经常有人建议……所谓的“青年凸起”，使国家更容易受到政治暴力的影响……这一主张在1950  -  2000年期间的时间序列跨国统计模型中经过经验测试。以及1984  -  1995年恐怖主义和骚乱的事件数据。人们对青年隆起的期望应该增加政治暴力的风险，从而获得了对所有三种形式的暴力的强有力的支持。</p></blockquote><p> <a href="https://www.cfr.org/report/family-planning-strategic-focus-us-foreign-policy">Madsen（2021）</a>写道：</p><blockquote><p> 1990年代的证据表明，十五至29岁的人占成年人口的40％以上的国家的可能性遭受了民间冲突的可能性是两倍。在1970年至2007年之间，在所有民间冲突爆发中，有80％发生在至少60％的人口年轻30岁以下的国家中……只有少数国家被评为民主国家，并且对政治自由，腐败和限制机构能力弱也很普遍。从1950年到2000年收集的数据发现，其中35％或更多的成年人口包括十五至二十四岁的人，遭受民间冲突爆发的可能性高150％。在持续高生育率的国家的情况下，相关性最强。一旦人口过渡得以完全进行，即使由于过去高水平的生育能力，人们的冲突爆发爆发的可能性就较小。</p></blockquote><p><a href="https://erf.org.eg/app/uploads/2019/06/1310.pdf">易卜拉欣（2019）</a>和其他人发现了类似的结果。与往常一样，这是<a href="https://www.newsecuritybeat.org/2018/04/age-structure-intra-state-conflict-imagined/">对理论的批评者</a>，一些作者基于不同类型的冲突进行了区分，例如， <a href="https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Dan-Miodownik/publication/265650970_Youth_bulge_and_civil_war_Why_a_country's_share_of_young_adults_explains_only_non-ethnic_wars/links/5ad50cf9a6fdcc2935809baa/Youth-bulge-and-civil-war-Why-a-countrys-share-of-young-adults-explains-only-non-ethnic-wars.pdf">Yair和Midownik（2014）</a>声称，青年的凸起与“种族战争”不那么相关，而Cincotta和Weber（2021年） ）警告说，他们的结果很难测试“分离主义”战争。但是，尽管如此，该领域的普遍共识似乎是一个非常年轻的人群与不稳定和暴力相关。</p><p>关于为什么青年凸起可能引起冲突的理论有多种理论。在非常贫穷的国家，资源稀缺是一个明显的因素。在其他国家，有一种理论，即青年隆起会给年轻人带来更少的经济和社会机会 - 基本上，年轻人互相挤出来，这使他们发疯。当经济停滞不前时，这种影响显然会加剧。另外，仅仅让很多年轻人没有太多损失似乎是一个危险因素。</p><p>中东停滞的经济体显然是整个地区席卷暴力行为的一个因素（尽管那里显然有双向因果关系）。无论是富人还是穷人，大中东的国家 - 我将把阿富汗和巴基斯坦扔到混合中，因为它们也是一个很大的冲突源 - 只是根本不会经历太多的经济增长。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg" width="684" height="490.8705882352941" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:732,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:684,&quot;bytes&quot;:131841,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>但是，至少从避免冲突的角度来看，这里的好消息是这些国家正在稳步增长。该地区有许多国家的中位年龄已经超过25年的国家： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89508d3f-6114-4cf3-8420-2c91d4895ee1_1020x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89508d3f-6114-4cf3-8420-2c91d4895ee1_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89508d3f-6114-4cf3-8420-2c91d4895ee1_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89508d3f-6114-4cf3-8420-2c91d4895ee1_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89508d3f-6114-4cf3-8420-2c91d4895ee1_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89508d3f-6114-4cf3-8420-2c91d4895ee1_1020x720.jpeg" width="1020" height="720" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89508d3f-6114-4cf3-8420-2c91d4895ee1_1020x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:124007,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89508d3f-6114-4cf3-8420-2c91d4895ee1_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89508d3f-6114-4cf3-8420-2c91d4895ee1_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89508d3f-6114-4cf3-8420-2c91d4895ee1_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89508d3f-6114-4cf3-8420-2c91d4895ee1_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>看这张图表并意识到发生了多少事情，这真是令人震惊。当伊朗在1980年代的“<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Operation_Ramadan">人类浪潮</a>”袭击中向伊拉克投掷成千上万的士兵时，伊朗中位数只有17岁。现在，伊朗人中位数正处于30年代初。这可能是伊朗从直接交战转移到诸如霍西斯，真主党和哈马斯之类的代理民兵的原因之一。沙特阿拉伯参与了也门战争，但不愿派遣地面部队对阵胡希斯（Houthis） - 可能是因为胡希斯（Houthis）是强大的，但可能是因为沙特人的年轻人相对较少。</p><p>同样， <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Algerian_Civil_War">90年代阿尔及利亚</a>和<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lebanese_Civil_War">80年代黎巴嫩的</a>可怕内战发生在这些国家比今天年轻得多的时候。真主党居住在一个比2006年袭击以色列的年龄较大的国家，这可能与为什么他们坐在这个国家中有关。在此名单上的所有国家中，只有利比亚发生了相对较新的战争。</p><p>另一方面，该地区还有许多其他国家还很年轻： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fee09d28e-5aa4-48d6-aae1-430d2b72ddbd_1020x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fee09d28e-5aa4-48d6-aae1-430d2b72ddbd_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fee09d28e-5aa4-48d6-aae1-430d2b72ddbd_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fee09d28e-5aa4-48d6-aae1-430d2b72ddbd_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fee09d28e-5aa4-48d6-aae1-430d2b72ddbd_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fee09d28e-5aa4-48d6-aae1-430d2b72ddbd_1020x720.jpeg" width="1020" height="720" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ee09d28e-5aa4-48d6-aae1-430d2b72ddbd_1020x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:131194,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fee09d28e-5aa4-48d6-aae1-430d2b72ddbd_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fee09d28e-5aa4-48d6-aae1-430d2b72ddbd_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fee09d28e-5aa4-48d6-aae1-430d2b72ddbd_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fee09d28e-5aa4-48d6-aae1-430d2b72ddbd_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>我认为，过去十年中大多数发生战争的中东国家都在此名单上也就不足为奇了。它们还包括伊朗拥有代理人（黎巴嫩除外）的几乎所有国家。令人不安的是，阿富汗，也门，巴勒斯坦，伊拉克和巴基斯坦预计从现在起十年的中位年龄仍低于中位数。</p><p>但这就是说，所有这些国家仍在稳定的剪辑中衰老 - 已经超过25岁的国家也是如此。基本原因是大中东（以及整个更广泛的穆斯林世界）生育率的崩溃很大过去几十年。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8fc66ca-f892-4624-9190-805e00face00_1020x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8fc66ca-f892-4624-9190-805e00face00_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8fc66ca-f892-4624-9190-805e00face00_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8fc66ca-f892-4624-9190-805e00face00_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8fc66ca-f892-4624-9190-805e00face00_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8fc66ca-f892-4624-9190-805e00face00_1020x720.jpeg" width="680" height="480" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f8fc66ca-f892-4624-9190-805e00face00_1020x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:680,&quot;bytes&quot;:150769,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8fc66ca-f892-4624-9190-805e00face00_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8fc66ca-f892-4624-9190-805e00face00_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8fc66ca-f892-4624-9190-805e00face00_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8fc66ca-f892-4624-9190-805e00face00_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p> （该数据源没有巴勒斯坦，但<a href="https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/fertility-rate-with-projections?time=1980..2033&amp;country=AFG~PSE~ISR~YEM~SYR~IRQ~LBY">联合国以3.5的速度显示</a>。）</p><p>同样，考虑其中一些数字是非常令人震惊的。当伊朗在革命中爆炸并在70年代后期和80年代与伊拉克进行了泰坦尼克号战争时，其生育能力超过6岁。现在下降到约1.5。当美国在2001年入侵阿富汗时，其生育能力超过7。现在，它低于4。（顺便说一句，查看该统计数据，问自己美国职业是否可能比您想象的要取得的成就更多。）</p><p>下降的生育能力似乎也从青年隆起中脱颖而出，即使一个国家还很年轻。乌尔达（2006）写道：</p><blockquote><p>在持续的高生育和高依赖性的背景下，青年凸起，使国家越来越有可能遇到武装冲突……而人口过渡的国家正在进行，可能会遇到“和平股息”。</p></blockquote><p>无论如何，我不想在这里声称“人口统计学是命运”，而且看着各个国家并讲述衰老和生育能力可能影响他们的冲突的故事太容易了。即使老年人和较少的儿童确实使战争的可能性降低了，但饱受战争war的国家（阿富汗，也门，伊拉克，巴勒斯坦和叙利亚）仍然很年轻，但仍然具有相当强大的生育能力。</p><p>但是，很难不看这些图，并觉得大事正在改变。老年中东，大批愤怒的年轻人在街上挤满了人，准备爆炸为民族主义者，宗派或革命性暴力，正在稳步消失，被一个更加镇定的衰老社会所取代。考虑到过去几十年的可怕结果，很难不认为这是一件好事。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButt