44,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F13f69f8a-966e-4534-8957-770bb4166995_1601x1221.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F13f69f8a-966e-4534-8957-770bb4166995_1601x1221.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F13f69f8a-966e-4534-8957-770bb4166995_1601x1221.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F13f69f8a-966e-4534-8957-770bb4166995_1601x1221.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://howmuch.net/articles/us-exports-imports-trade-balance">whowmuch.net</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>而且，由于南亚和东南亚的迅速增长，该地区对美国经济的重要性<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-next-phase-of-globalization-is">只会增长</a>，即使我们继续与中国脱钩。</p><p>同时，中东作为贸易伙伴绝对很小。特别是，美国根本不依赖中东油。多亏了压裂，我们是<a href="https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-poised-become-net-exporter-crude-oil-2023-2022-12-19/">原油的净出口国</a>。沙特阿拉伯，阿联酋和科威特可能会被哥斯拉食用，我们的炼油厂只会嗡嗡作响。 （顺便说一句，美国石油生产<a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/08/09/business/oil-production-biden-trump/index.html">只是在拜登的领导下创造了新的记录</a>。）</p><p>现在，确实，我们的一些盟友，例如日本和韩国，仍然购买了很多中东石油。而且，如果对中东石油供应有很大的干扰，全球价格将大量上涨，这会导致美国石油生产商的意外收获，但伤害了其他类型的美国业务。但是<a href="https://about.bnef.com/blog/electric-cars-have-dented-fuel-demand-by-2040-theyll-slash-it/">，由于电动汽车的兴起</a>，石油对全球经济的重要性变得不那么重要。预测，总油耗很快就会平坦。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg" width="655" height="398" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:398,&quot;width&quot;:655,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:65391,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：IEA</figcaption></figure></div><p>相对于电动汽车和其他替代品提高石油价格的中东冲突只会加速这一趋势。</p><p>因此，即使亚洲继续变得更加至关重要，中东对美国的经济重要性迅速减少。削减美国的亚洲经济超级聚集将深深地损害我们国家的繁荣，而在中东我们确实不再需要很多。</p><p>因此，美国应继续保持在中东的存在。这并不意味着我们应该完全撤回。在极端情况下，明智的，有针对性的美国权力应用可以防止一些经常困扰该地区的灾难 - 保护叙利亚库尔德人免受种族灭绝的侵害，限制以色列对巴勒斯坦人的残酷行为，或帮助以色列免受伊朗及其批发销毁的侵害代理。但是，这些应始终以最少的力量，金钱和关注来完成，并始终注视再次撤离。</p><p>与此同时，在亚洲，美国应该加强我们的防御能力和与其他国家的互动。我们需要加速向台湾，日本，越南，印度和菲律宾加速防御性武器，并继续建造，加强和扩大诸如Quad之类的多边组织。我们需要通过<a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/japan-wants-u-s-back-in-the-tpp-it-will-likely-have-to-wait-11618570801">重新加入经过改进的TPP</a>并建立亚洲其他经济协议的密集网络来经济地重新参与。总的来说，我们只需要对该地区大量关注，确保我们的盟友和准盟友和潜在的盟友知道我们很长一段时间就在那里，并且不会突然撤回陷入一些愚蠢的事情中东的冲突。</p><p>即使面对以色列 - 加沙战争和其他分裂，情感上的令人难以置信的头条冲突，拜登政府及其继任者也需要很多纪律和许多解释。但是无论如何我们都必须这样做。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/asia-is-much-more-important-to-us?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/asia-is-much-more-important-to-us?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p>; 
