n102">与埃里克·托伦伯格（Erik Torenberg）的Econ 102</a>的两集。这是一个相当黑暗而可怕的情节，讲述了第三次世界大战的危险和Pax Americana的终结： </p><iframe class="spotify-wrap podcast" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6765630000ba8a989dc76846ca8ca068ddca77&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;E15: Why Pax Americana is Dying and What Happens if China Attacks Taiwan&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith, Erik Torenberg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Episode&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/episode/2Mmd4IubcxLV946z5PvtTQ&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/2Mmd4IubcxLV946z5PvtTQ" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>这是<a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/e15-why-pax-americana-is-dying-and-what-happens-if/id1696419056?i=1000631790527">Apple播客</a>和<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b72fspwaOUU">YouTube</a>链接，以防您不碰巧使用Spotify。</p><p>这是关于技术乐观主义的相当愉快而乐观的情节： </p><iframe class="spotify-wrap podcast" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6765630000ba8aa2e60a8e34ce6b48a1073805&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;E16: Techno-Optimism, Nuclear Energy, and How To Enable More Innovation&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith, Erik Torenberg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Episode&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/episode/5GtFZ6ADPlVGKWYyKRrE1T&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/5GtFZ6ADPlVGKWYyKRrE1T" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>以下是该播客的<a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/be/podcast/e16-techno-optimism-nuclear-energy-and-how-to-enable/id1696419056?i=1000632407152">Apple 播客</a>和<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dIYfLd10ZfA">YouTube</a>链接。</p><p>这是我对Techno-Sbeatpicchad Haag进行的有关Lev Polyakov的技术乐观主义的辩论： </p><div id="youtube2-9iY7_fr-5c